  'terms-article-5': 'Article 5 – RETURN, REFUND, CANCELLATION ',
  'terms-article-5-p1':
    'Custom configured, personalized or other products cannot be returned for refund or exchange under any circumstances, unless the product is damaged.- Please note that Terre54 does not allow returns or refunds on the following products:- Products custom configured to your specifications, including personalized products.- Edible and perishable products- What should I do if an item is delivered damaged?- If the item appears to have been obviously damaged by the shipper, tell the driver immediately that you do not want to receive the package. If the damaged package was left behind or someone else signed for it, there is a grace period of about 3 days to file a claim. If a package appears suspiciously damaged, you can ask the driver to wait and open the package to make sure the contents are not damaged and, if they are, to refuse the package and claim the damage. Obtain a control number from the shipper and contact us at',
